Ondo Governor Rotimi Akeredolu has declared his is ready for any form of primary his party, the All Progressives Congress (APC) adopts. Akeredolu spoke with State House Correspondents on Tuesday after meeting with President Muhammadu Buhari at the Presidential Villa in Abuja. Asked if he was confident of winning the party primaries, the Governor said he was sure God would give him victory. Akeredolu said he was in the State House to tell Buhari he was running for re-election and to present his Expression of Interest forms to him. Details shortlyâ€¦